42
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,520
why aren't these records

43
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:41,910
in the dossier?

44
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:48,440
At that time,
murders happened frequently.

45
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:50,240
All autopsies were simply done.

46
00:02:50,470 --> 00:02:52,630
We had to rush
to the next crime scene after that.

47
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,630
After the magistrate closed the case,

48
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:56,960
I still couldn't forget these cases.

49
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:59,160
So I secretly did some investigations

50
00:02:59,270 --> 00:03:00,390
and found some evidence.

51
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:03,550
When I presented the conclusion
of the investigation,

52
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:05,270
that useless magistrate

53
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:08,720
thought my conclusion was too bizarre.

54
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:10,110
He said I was crazy.

55
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:14,270
Nobody believed in me.

56
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,670
Master,
what about the next four victims?

57
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:20,520
Here, look.

58
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:22,520
They were also

59
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:25,520
victims of the same mystifying method.

60
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:38,720
This victim

61
00:03:39,270 --> 00:03:41,110
is the eighth victim.

62
00:03:41,830 --> 00:03:42,390
Master,

63
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,960
