we want to investigate.

64
00:03:44,390 --> 00:03:45,910
She might be the one
who wrote to my father back then.

65
00:03:48,110 --> 00:03:49,000
I remember her.

66
00:03:52,630 --> 00:03:55,600
Back then,
on my way home from the county yamen,

67
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:59,550
I used to always pass by the tea house
where she worked.

68
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:02,160
Miss Shang was enchanting,

69
00:04:02,390 --> 00:04:04,080
and she left a deep impression on me.

70
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:07,320
Who would have thought

71
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,110
she had the most tragic death?

72
00:04:09,110 --> 00:04:10,440
[Gen, Mountain, Burning Execution]

73
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,720
When she was still alive,

74
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:15,720
she must have been
drenched in boiling molten copper.

75
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:21,760
So, at the time of her death,

76
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:24,880
she must have suffered terribly.

77
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:29,300
[Pouring molten copper
on a living person as a mold]

78
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,670
Master,

79
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,480
do all these cases

80
00:04:34,550 --> 00:04:36,880
have something to do with Heavenly
Master Lu from the Luoyun Sect?

81
00:04:38,110 --> 00:04:39,640
Definitely yes.

82
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:43,720
Caiwei, do you still remember

83
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,640
that one night with heavy rain

84
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,950
when I came home almost at dawn?

85
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,920
My clothes were full of blood.

86
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,040
Yes, I do.

87
00:04:54,790 --> 00:04:57,040
But you told me
that you had fallen accidentally.

88
00:04:59,550 --> 00:05:00,670
Actually,

89
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,230
that night,

90
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:05,160
I secretly went
to the back mountain of the Luoyun Sect.

91
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:08,670
I quietly dug up
Heavenly Master Lu's grave.

92
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,640
I found a female corpse inside.

93
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:15,720
The time of her death
matched the previous statement.

94
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,070
Too bad,

95
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:20,160
before I got the chance
to examine it thoroughly,

96
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,880
the sect leader,
Xue Jianli, discovered me.

97
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,070
He tried to kill me

98
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,230
and spared me no life.

99
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:26,920
He injured me.

100
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:29,110
But I was lucky enough

101
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:30,320
to escape.

102
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,950
It's weird.

103
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,600
If nothing were wrong with the corpse,

104
00:05:36,110 --> 00:05:37,830
why would Xue Jianli try to kill you?

105
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,440
After Heavenly Master Lu's death,

106
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:45,270
the Luoyun Sect used
the resurrection of Heavenly Master Lu

107
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:47,350
to attract a large number of followers.

108
00:05:48,110 --> 00:05:50,920
I guess he was afraid
of being discovered

109
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,790
that Heavenly Master Lu's corpse was
no different from an ordinary person's,

110
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:57,320
which would debunk the myth.

111
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,110
That's the reason.

112
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,480
Is there a possibility

113
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:05,070
that Xue Jianli is the culprit?

114
00:06:05,790 --> 00:06:07,790
He used Heavenly Master Lu as a cover

115
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,110
and then profited from it.

116
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,670
You're right!

117
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,790
I also think so.

118
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:15,070
Only can this explain why,

119
00:06:15,350 --> 00:06:16,480
after Heavenly Master Lu's death,

120
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:18,640
there were still people
being killed one after another.

121
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:20,790
It looks like

122
00:06:22,110 --> 00:06:23,550
we need to visit the Luoyun Sect.

123
00:06:26,340 --> 00:06:29,220
[Luoyun Sect]

124
00:06:41,220 --> 00:06:43,940
[Xue Jianli, the leader of Luoyun Sect]

125
00:06:57,600 --> 00:07:00,790
Miss, why are they praying there?

126
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,790
Is the Luoyun Sect
really that effective?

127
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,390
Of course.

128
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,270
Let me tell you,

129
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:06,640
I come here every year.

130
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,160
This Master Xue

131
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:09,920
has a very profound cultivation.

132
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,790
As long as we pray sincerely,

133
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,200
our wishes

134
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:14,640
will be fulfilled.

135
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:18,110
Especially your wish,

136
00:07:18,230 --> 00:07:18,920
which will be fulfilled effectively.

137
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,640
How do you know
what we're going to wish for?

138
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,270
It's so obvious.

139
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,790
You two are obviously newlyweds.

140
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:26,160
Are you here to wish for a child?

141
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:30,550
Let me tell you both.

142
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,920
As long as the two of you

143
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,440
spend a night
in the Luoyun Sect's fasting room.

144
00:07:34,790 --> 00:07:35,640
I guarantee

145
00:07:35,790 --> 00:07:37,720
that the two of you

146
00:07:37,790 --> 00:07:39,200
will become three persons
when you leave.

147
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:40,830
It's not that. I...

148
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,200
She's right, dear.

149
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:44,510
It suits us well.

150
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,440
Let's join them.

151
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,920
Come on, let's get in line.

152
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:58,200
How long have you been married?

153
00:07:59,110 --> 00:08:00,200
Over three months.

154
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:03,110
Just over three months,
and you're already in such a hurry.

155
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,110
You're really impatient.

156
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:08,640
She's not in a hurry,

157
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:10,230
but I am.

158
00:08:10,550 --> 00:08:12,200
It's not easy to marry her.

159
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:14,270
I have to quickly have a child
and establish a family.

160
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:17,320
Don't overact.

161
00:08:19,350 --> 00:08:20,440
I'm sorry, dear.

162
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,230
It's my fault.

163
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:22,350
I won't dare to do it again.

164
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,440
Miss,

165
00:08:27,790 --> 00:08:29,200
