and good times♪

454
00:29:12,820 --> 00:29:19,420
♪Listening to the promises, I could feel
tender warmth at my fingertips♪

455
00:29:24,830 --> 00:29:26,280
When I expressed my love,

456
00:29:27,310 --> 00:29:28,920
he said we were only
a master and a disciple.

457
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:30,560
Considering the views of other people,

458
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:32,000
he rejected me.

459
00:29:33,190 --> 00:29:34,400
I didn't want to let him go,

460
00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:36,230
so I changed my name.

461
00:29:37,520 --> 00:29:39,400
I'm not afraid
to let others know my thoughts.

462
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:42,280
I loved only him.

