470
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:02,950
He just didn't have the courage
to admit it.

471
00:30:04,310 --> 00:30:06,040
But human sacrifice,

472
00:30:08,070 --> 00:30:09,160
this method is evil.

473
00:30:10,070 --> 00:30:11,110
He and I agreed

474
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:13,760
