in our lifetime.

475
00:30:15,350 --> 00:30:16,560
But who would have thought...

476
00:30:24,230 --> 00:30:25,000
Master!

477
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:36,470
Master, you promised!

478
00:30:36,710 --> 00:30:38,920
This method is evil.
We must never use it in our lifetime.

479
00:30:39,110 --> 00:30:40,590
I have no choice.

480
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:42,520
But that doesn't mean
you can sacrifice lives.

481
00:30:43,070 --> 00:30:45,190
Master, trust me.

482
00:30:45,430 --> 00:30:47,350
There must be another way
to cure your injury.

483
00:30:48,350 --> 00:30:49,000
Please?

484
00:30:54,430 --> 00:30:55,000
All right.

485
00:30:56,800 --> 00:30:58,280
