to the ancient book hall now.

486
00:31:01,710 --> 00:31:03,800
I'll attract attention
if I disappear out of thin air.

487
00:31:04,350 --> 00:31:05,760
Xue Jianli used the Breath-Pausing Pill

488
00:31:05,760 --> 00:31:07,310
