left some clues at the murder scene.

491
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,800
He cast all the suspicion

492
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:16,040
onto me, a dead person.

493
00:31:17,280 --> 00:31:18,640
He locked me in the dungeon

494
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:22,760
