508
00:31:53,280 --> 00:31:54,110
I didn't want to help him,

509
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:56,800
so he used pills to control my mind.

510
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:01,640
By the way,

511
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:06,000
Xue Jianli chose
these eight women as sacrifices.

512
00:32:06,310 --> 00:32:07,560
Are there any reasons?

513
00:32:09,590 --> 00:32:10,830
According to ancient records,

514
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:14,040
